            "answer_text": "If actual price is x, Then A sold book to B for 1.2x with 20% profit. That is x+ 20% of x = 1.2x. Then B sold book to C for 1.32x with 10% profit. That is 1.2x+ 10%of 1.2x =1.32x. So C bought it for $396 which is 1.32x. That is 1.32x=396, x=300. So actual price or A bought it for $300. ",
